abstract: Caroline Wozniacki beats Ana Konjuh in first round at Qatar Open; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: Wozniacki struggled to beat the Croatian qualifier Ana Konjuh at the Qatar Open in Doha, avoiding a third opening loss in her past four tournaments.

headline.main: Caroline Wozniacki Avoids Upset in Qatar
